snippet.title: Mortal Kombat II | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's called Mortal Kombat (II).
Mortal Kombat II – only in theaters and @imax October 24. #MortalKombatMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favorite champions—now joined by Johnny Cage himself—are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/Broken Road Production, a Fireside Films Production, Mortal Kombat II.  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAX® across North America on October 24, 2025, and internationally beginning 22 October 2025.

snippet.title: Tron: Ares | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the brand-new trailer for Tron: Ares and experience it in theaters, filmed for IMAX, October 10.
 
Tron: Ares follows a highly sophisticated Program, Ares, who is sent from the digital world into the real world on a dangerous mission, marking humankind’s first encounter with A.I. beings. The feature film is directed by Joachim Rønning and stars Jared Leto, Greta Lee, Evan Peters, Hasan Minhaj, Jodie Turner-Smith, Arturo Castro, Cameron Monaghan, with Gillian Anderson, and Jeff Bridges. Sean Bailey, Jeffrey Silver, Justin Springer, Jared Leto, Emma Ludbrook and Steven Lisberger are the producers, with Russell Allen serving as executive producer.

Grammy®-award winning rock band Nine Inch Nails composed the score for “Tron: Ares,” and today, the band dropped "As Alive As You Need Me To Be" —the soundtrack album’s first single and the first official music from the band in five years. Listen to "As Alive As You Need Me To Be” and view the visualizer: https://nineinchnails.lnk.to/AAAYNMTB. The track is featured in the new trailer for “Tron: Ares.”
 
“Tron: Ares (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack),” featuring all original music by Nine Inch Nails, will be released on September 19 via Interscope Records. The release marks the first-ever film score by the pioneering band, although bandmates Trent Reznor and Atticus Ross have composed 20 scores under their own names, winning two Oscars®, three Golden Globes®, a GRAMMY® and an Emmy® in the process.
 
ALBUM: https://NineInchNails.lnk.to/TRONAres
SINGLE: https://NineInchNails.lnk.to/AAAYNMTB

snippet.title: Stranger Things 5 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every battle has led to this.

More about Stranger Things 5:
The fall of 1987. Hawkins is scarred by the opening of the Rifts, and our heroes are united by a single goal: find and kill Vecna. But he has vanished — his whereabouts and plans unknown. Complicating their mission, the government has placed the town under military quarantine and intensified its hunt for Eleven, forcing her back into hiding. As the anniversary of Will’s disappearance approaches, so does a heavy, familiar dread. The final battle is looming — and with it, a darkness more powerful and more deadly than anything they’ve faced before. To end this nightmare, they’ll need everyone — the full party — standing together, one last time.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81297917

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 2 - Official 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer (2025) Karl Urban
snippet.description:
Don't miss the 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer for Mortal Kombat 2, the upcoming action film based on the hit Mortal Kombat game IP distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures. Take a look at the in-universe film trailer for Uncaged Fury starring the one and only Johnny Cage, portrayed by Karl Urban. 

Uncaged Fury sees the legendary Johnny Cage take on a band of goons with ease, making use of pipes, fast-paced combat skills, and an aura unlike any other.

Mortal Kombat 2 is in theaters on October 24.

snippet.title: ‘Love Island USA’: Nic & Olandria Give Relationship Update Outside The Villa
snippet.description:
Nic and Olandria are spilling the tea! In their first interview together outside the villa, the pair look back with Access Hollywood’s Lauren Herbert on their journey to romance on “Love Island USA.” Nic and Olandria share their favorite things about one another and give an update to their relationship. Plus, they share if they wish they got together sooner and talk about upcoming reunion.

snippet.title: Reuniting With My Family and Girlfriend After 2 Years
snippet.description:
MY BROTHER IS HOME!! 😭✈️ Emotional Missionary Homecoming After 2 Years

After two years away, Brock is finally HOME!! He spent the last year and a half serving in Boston, Massachusetts, and this vlog captures the unforgettable moments leading up to his return. From packing his (very heavy) bags and saying goodbye to mission friends, to getting paired with a final companion—his journey back was emotional and full of meaning.

Back at home, I was getting everything ready for his arrival—stocking the pantry (per Brock’s special request), grabbing some of his favorite foods, and prepping the house for a big surprise. We stayed up late making posters (yes, including a hilarious “marry me” one and some Fortnite-themed signs 😂) and decorated everything to make his homecoming extra special.

He landed in Salt Lake City, and the moment he walked through those airport doors… we were all in tears. Our mom cried, and the biggest surprise of all—his girlfriend was there to meet him even though he thought she’d still be out of town 👀

Once we got home, Brock saw his room for the first time, opened his welcome-back gift basket, and we wrapped up the perfect day with a Bees baseball game as a family. It was one of those days we’ll never forget. 

Video’s/Things mentioned: 
- Amazon Storefront (Favorite products): https://amzlink.to/az02wwSvCTCHc
- LTK (Where we link our outfits): https://www.shopltk.com/explore/brockandboston
- Discount Codes: https://shopmy.us/brockandboston

I dare you to tap me: https://brockandboston.com/links/

Meet Brock and Boston:
What’s up!!! We are twin brothers from Salt Lake City, Utah that recently moved to Nashville, Tennessee. We started doing social media back in 2016 and have been posting ever since. We love sharing our life with everyone! On our channel, we do a mix of a lot of things like challenges, vlogs, pranks, and more! 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Social Media Accounts:

Instagram: @brockandbostonofficial 

TikTok: @brockandboston 

Twitter: @brockandboston

Facebook: @brockandboston 

--------------------------------------------

Our family’s channels:

Brock and Boston Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE7S... 

Alyssa & Dallin: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpKW... 


The Mikesell Family: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmZN... 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Q&A: 

Are you twins? Yes, we are Identical twins! 

How do I tell you apart? Brock currently has a mullet, you will for sure be able to tell us apart after watching a few videos! 

Who is the older twin? Brock, by two minutes! 

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mailing Address:

 5491 W Hammerfest Way, Ste 201
South Jordan, UT 84009

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Contact Information for business inquiries: 


brockandboston@gmail.com

snippet.title: We Spent 48 Hours With MLB All-Stars!
snippet.description:
We Spent 2 Days with MLB All-Stars at the 95th All-Star Game in Atlanta, Georgia! We hope you enjoy this video and consider subscribing if you do, it really helps us out! 🦾

We’ve got an action packed video this week as we attended the Home Run Derby and All-Star Game, along with media day and the red carpet show. We saw familiar faces and met a bunch of guys for the first time and got to congratulate them on their All-Star nomination, which was so cool. We had a bunch of interviews and hilarious moments throughout the entire trip, so be sure to stick around to the end of the video!

We said what’s up and interviewed a bunch of players from both the National League and American League, including; Kyle Tucker, Pete Crow-Armstrong, Aroldis Chapman, Logan Webb, Corbin Carroll, Jacob Misiorowski, Jazz Chisholm Jr., Byron Buxton, Steven Kwan, MacKenzie Gore, James Wood, Jacob Wilson, Brendon Donovan, Ryan O’Hearn, Hunter Goodman, Brandon Lowe, Zach McKinstry, 

Thank you so much to all of the players for their time, we’re so excited to see how all of them continue to ball out in the second half. Also thank you so much to MLB for giving us credentialed access to talk to the games biggest stars on the biggest stage. Finally, thank you to you all for your continued support ❤️ none of this is possible without you guys and we are so grateful to be able to go on these adventures because of you all. Shoutout to everyone that said what’s up to us on the trip, Atlanta was amazing. Stay tuned as we’ve got a LOT more content coming the rest of the summer💯


If you enjoyed this video and want to see more like it, make sure to SUBSCRIBE! The support from everyone who watches our videos means so much to us and we're going to continue to grind to promote the incredible game of baseball and all the culture and personalities within it!

SUBSCRIBE: https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCV9bUn2gOlnMHpYNbohxYaA

Follow us on INSTAGRAM and TIK TOK @batboysbaseball for the coolest  baseball content you’re going to find!!!!

INSTAGRAM: https://instagram.com/batboysbaseball
TIK TOK: https://vm.tiktok.com/wgsBao/

en.title: We Spent 48 Hours With MLB All-Stars!
en.description:
We Spent 2 Days with MLB All-Stars at the 95th All-Star Game in Atlanta, Georgia! We hope you enjoy this video and consider subscribing if you do, it really helps us out! 🦾

We’ve got an action packed video this week as we attended the Home Run Derby and All-Star Game, along with media day and the red carpet show. We saw familiar faces and met a bunch of guys for the first time and got to congratulate them on their All-Star nomination, which was so cool. We had a bunch of interviews and hilarious moments throughout the entire trip, so be sure to stick around to the end of the video!

We said what’s up and interviewed a bunch of players from both the National League and American League, including; Kyle Tucker, Pete Crow-Armstrong, Aroldis Chapman, Logan Webb, Corbin Carroll, Jacob Misiorowski, Jazz Chisholm Jr., Byron Buxton, Steven Kwan, MacKenzie Gore, James Wood, Jacob Wilson, Brendon Donovan, Ryan O’Hearn, Hunter Goodman, Brandon Lowe, Zach McKinstry, 

Thank you so much to all of the players for their time, we’re so excited to see how all of them continue to ball out in the second half. Also thank you so much to MLB for giving us credentialed access to talk to the games biggest stars on the biggest stage. Finally, thank you to you all for your continued support ❤️ none of this is possible without you guys and we are so grateful to be able to go on these adventures because of you all. snippet.description:

snippet.title: Why Modern Gaming Sucks - You Own Nothing, And You're Not Happy
snippet.description: Live service models. Endless updates. Microtransactions. Mandatory patches. Always online. Gaming has become a bloated, money-grabbing disaster where you increasingly don't even own the game you've supposedly bought. And at any moment, the company who rent it to you could decide to shut it down. Is it any wonder the Stop Killing Games movement has become so huge, so quickly?

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS Season 5 TRAILER Explained
snippet.description:
I review, breakdown and explain Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer. I give my reaction to the new official teaser for the final season. I discuss the new clips in the preview which showed Vecna returning and looking different, Jonathan potentially dying in the upside down, Will being connected to The Mind Flayer and being taken by Vecna, Eddie's grave being defaced, the return of the Demodogs, the portal in Hawkins Library to the upside down and the final battle with Vecna and Eleven. I give my theories and predictions on what could happen to Mike, Lucas, Dustin, Nancy, Robin, the new characters, The Mind Flayer, Hopper, Joyce, Robin, the ending and the release date.

snippet.title: The 'Zombies 4' Cast Talk Co-Star Crushes & Cringe Auditions | Pass the Popcorn | Seventeen
snippet.description:
Milo Manheim, Meg Donnelly, Malachi Barton, and Freya Skye are trading zombies and fangs for brutally honest confessions in this episode of “Pass the Popcorn.” Can the ‘Zombies 4: Dawn of the Vampires’ cast handle the heat offscreen as they face a mouthful of shady questions (and popcorn)? With only one pass allowed, nothing is off-limits as they call out each other’s toxic traits, expose cringe audition memories, and reveal the wildest DMs they’ve ever received. Between bites, the co-stars open up about awkward fan run-ins, debate which DCOMs are lowkey overrated, and—spoiler alert—someone admits they’ve never even watched the ‘Zombies’ movies outside of the premiere 👀.
 
Stream ‘Zombies 4: Dawn of the Vampires’ on Disney+.

snippet.title: Love Island's Nic & Olandria APOLOGIZE to Nicolandria Nation After Denying Feelings for Each Other
snippet.description: 'Love Island USA' season 7 runners-up Nic Vansteenberghe and Olandria Carthen chat with ET's Brice Sander following the finale, now streaming on Peacock. The pair address denying their feelings for one another after a steamy kiss in Soul Ties, explaining it was a defense mechanism to protect the people they were then-interested in, Cierra Ortega and Taylor Williams. They share where they stand with the ex-Islanders now and whether they're ready to label each other boyfriend and girlfriend ahead of the soon-to-tape reunion, set to premiere on Aug. 25 on Peacock.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. snippet.title: Investigating the DKOldies Scam...
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more! https://www.youtube.com/austinevans
Check out our @thisis channel! https://www.youtube.com/thisis
As well as the @Denki channel! https://www.youtube.com/@Denki
Instagram: https://instagram.com/austinnotduncan
Threads: https://www.threads.net/@austinnotduncan

Is DKOldies REALLY the retro gaming paradise they claim to be? After spending over $1,300 on vintage consoles and games, the results were...not great. From broken Wii Us with cracked vents to Xbox 360s that literally scratch your discs, this investigation reveals what you're actually getting for your money. Plus, we test their warranty claims and trade-in process with some eye-opening results. Are they worth those premium prices or should you look elsewhere for your retro gaming fix?

0:00 Ordering
2:46 Unboxing
3:37 Wii U

7:55 PS2 Slim
11:06 GameCube
14:43 Xbox 360
17:50 Nintendo Switch
20:10 Trade In and Warranty
23:33 Xbox 360 Round 2
24:53 Wii U Round 2
26:27 Conclusion

snippet.title: Ready or Not PS5 Review - A MUST PLAY Shooter
snippet.description:
A highly realistic, unerringly brutal tactical first-person shooter, that too with a good single-player component, is a tough call. Now try finding one inspired by one of the greatest of all time. the SWAT series, while standing out on its own.

Despite these heavy expectations and a somewhat repetitive campaign, Void Interactive's Ready or Not surprisingly steps up. As the leader of D Platoon, players embark on a harrowing journey through various missions, from robberies and busts to shootouts in deadly cabins rigged with traps. The gunplay is realistic, the tactics feel sound, and the presentation, especially the environments, is gritty and real.

Some iffy AI and a somewhat samey gameplay loop tend to bog things down, but thankfully, there's also co-op, where up to five players can team together for some chaotic fun. While Ready or Not won't revolutionize the genre, it does deserve some credit for going beyond simply paying tribute and delivering a worthwhile experience, even on consoles.

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

snippet.title: Jeff Teague REACTS to Bronny James BIG night, Cal Raleigh WINS Home Run Derby | 520 in the Morning
snippet.description:
On the Tuesday, July 15 episode of 520 in the Morning, Jeff Teague, DJ Wells, and B Hen react to Bronny James’ big night from NBA Summer League despite the Los Angeles Lakers losing to the Los Angeles Clippers. The guys then highlight some of the top rookies like Kon Knueppel, Dylan Harper, and Noa Essengue. The guys then react to the MLB Home Run Derby as Cal Raleigh became the first catcher in MLB history to win the derby.

POV: You're watching ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires with the actual cast! Join Malachi, Freya, Meg, and Milo for the ultimate movie night as they react to the film and relive the wildest behind-the-scenes moments in this iconic ZOMBIES 4 watch party!

ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires available on Disney Channel and Disney+
https://ondisneyplus.disney.com/movie/zombies-4-dawn-of-the-vampires

Watch the next Disney ZOMBIES 4 video here: https://youtu.be/miW2r1XbiJ8

Watch ZOMBIES 4 on Disney Channel! And check out more ZOMBIES 4 content here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHAfvwqfR5OA47WZB3-79ORi1SjVfbnzB

Check out more Disney ZOMBIES videos here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiv1IUQDVSNK24tqIxEQUmKxFnqkp3Dud&si=ZcRORW673WUk3OTP

"Zombies 4" introduces two warring groups of monsters, Daywalkers and Vampires, who inhabit two spectacular new worlds: east and west Rayburn, a world of perpetual day and a world of perpetual night. It’s up to Zed and Addison to help these two groups of sworn enemies find peace and common ground before their worlds suffer catastrophic consequences.

"Descendants/Zombies: Worlds Collide Tour" is a one-of-a-kind interactive live concert experience coming to arenas across North America in Summer 2025. The tour will feature Kylie Cantrall, Freya Skye, Malia Baker, Malachi Barton, Dara Reneé, Joshua Colley and Mekonnen Knife.  Kicking off in San Diego, CA on July 17, the arena tour will celebrate the chart-topping music from Disney’s “Descendants” and “Zombies” movie franchises, inspiring families, and fans of all ages to dance, sing, and engage with their favorite stars. You can click here for more information on dates, locations, and tickets - disneynow.com/descendantszombiestour

#disneyzombies #zombies4 #disneychannel #disneychannelmusic

snippet.title: $200 Cash If Randy and I Can Finish This 30" Team Pizza Challenge in Maine!
snippet.description:
Teaming up with @RandySantel to take on the 30" Gridiron Team Pizza Challenge at End Zone Pizza in Augusta, Maine! Teams of 2 have just 45 minutes to finish a 30" one-topping pizza in order to earn their meal for free, a groovy t-shirt, $200 cash, and a spot up on the wall of fame! Hungry diners may also attempt this solo and are granted a 90 minute time limit. Randy and I were a couple of silly gooses, however, and tried to be the first team to finish with several toppings (we each ordered specialty pizzas; I opted for the Hawaiian, Randy opted for the Philly Cheesesteak). Could we make history?!
***
RP Strength Code: KILOS
RP Diet App Link: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
RP Hypertrophy App Link: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
WEBSITE: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
About Me:
I'm a 5'2 former women's physique bodybuilder on a mission to sample delicious foods from around the world! I tackle restaurant challenges, sample new food menus, and explore the unique eats in various cities. To balance out the calorie intake of weekly food challenges, I continue to pursue my love of fitness through bodybuilding, running, and spinning. 

FAQ:
**How do you not get fat?** 
Please check out my "Daily Diet" Playlist Here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Why do you shake so much?**
I have a genetic condition known as "non-essential tremors". That in combination with nerves, being hungry with lowered blood sugar, and a deep and profound love affair with caffeine, makes for a rather jittery start to a challenge.

**Are you and Randy married?** 
No, not yet! We got engaged on December 1, 2024 though and are excited for the future!

de-DE.title: 200 $ in bar, wenn Randy und ich diese 30-Zoll-Team-Pizza-Challenge in Maine beenden können!
de-DE.description:
Gemeinsam mit @RandySantel nehmt ihr an der 30" Gridiron Team Pizza Challenge bei End Zone Pizza in Augusta, Maine, teil! Zweierteams haben nur 45 Minuten Zeit, um eine 30-Zoll-Pizza mit einem Belag fertigzubacken und sich so ein kostenloses Essen, ein cooles T-Shirt, 200 $ in bar und einen Platz an der Wall of Fame zu verdienen! Hungrige Gäste können es auch alleine versuchen und haben dafür ein Zeitlimit von 90 Minuten. Randy und ich waren allerdings ein paar dumme Gänse und versuchten, als erstes Team mit mehreren Belägen fertig zu sein (wir bestellten jeweils Spezialpizzas; ich entschied mich für die Hawaiian, Randy für das Philly Cheesesteak). Können wir Geschichte schreiben?! ***
RP Strength Code: KILOS
Link zur RP Diet App: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
Link zur RP Hypertrophy App: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
WEBSITE: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
Über mich:
Ich bin eine 1,57 m große ehemalige Bodybuilderin und habe es mir zur Aufgabe gemacht, köstliche Gerichte aus aller Welt zu probieren! Ich nehme an Restaurant-Challenges teil, probiere neue Speisekarten aus und entdecke die einzigartigen Restaurants verschiedener Städte. Um die Kalorienzufuhr der wöchentlichen Food-Challenges auszugleichen, widme ich mich weiterhin meiner Fitness-Liebe durch Bodybuilding, Laufen und Spinning.

FAQ:
**Wie schaffst du es, nicht dick zu werden?**
Schau dir meine Playlist „Daily Diet“ hier an: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Warum zitterst du so stark?**
Ich leide unter einer genetischen Erkrankung namens „nicht-essentieller Tremor“. In Kombination mit Nervosität, Hungergefühl und niedrigem Blutzuckerspiegel sowie einer tiefen Liebe zu Koffein sorgt das für einen ziemlich nervösen Start in eine Herausforderung.

**Sind du und Randy verheiratet?**
Nein, noch nicht! Wir haben uns aber am 1. Dezember 2024 verlobt und freuen uns auf die Zukunft!

es-US.title: ¡$200 en efectivo si Randy y yo podemos terminar este desafío de pizza en equipo de 30" en Maine!
es-US.description:
¡Nos unimos a @RandySantel para participar en el desafío de pizza de 76 cm en End Zone Pizza en Augusta, Maine! Los equipos de 2 tienen solo 45 minutos para terminar una pizza de 76 cm con un solo ingrediente y ganar su comida gratis, una camiseta genial, $200 en efectivo y un lugar en el muro de la fama. Los comensales hambrientos también pueden intentarlo en solitario y tienen un límite de 90 minutos. Sin embargo, Randy y yo fuimos un par de tontos e intentamos ser el primer equipo en terminar con varios ingredientes (cada uno pidió pizzas especiales; yo opté por la hawaiana, Randy por la Philly Cheesesteak). ¿Podríamos hacer historia? ***
Código de Fuerza RP: KILOS
Enlace de la app RP Diet: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
Enlace de la app RP Hypertrophy: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
SITIO WEB: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
Sobre mí:
Soy una ex fisicoculturista de 1,57 m con la misión de probar deliciosas comidas de todo el mundo. Me enfrento a retos de restaurantes, pruebo nuevos menús y exploro las opciones gastronómicas únicas de varias ciudades. Para equilibrar la ingesta calórica de los retos semanales de comida, sigo cultivando mi pasión por el fitness a través del culturismo, el running y el spinning.

Preguntas frecuentes:
**¿Cómo no engordas?**
No te pierdas mi lista de reproducción "Dieta diaria" aquí: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**¿Por qué tiemblas tanto?**
Tengo una afección genética conocida como "temblores no esenciales". Esto, combinado con nerviosismo, hambre con niveles bajos de azúcar en sangre y una profunda pasión por la cafeína, me hace empezar este reto con bastante nerviosismo.

Hongerige gasten mogen dit ook alleen proberen en krijgen daarvoor een tijdslimiet van 90 minuten. Randy en ik waren echter een stelletje domme ganzen en probeerden als eerste team met meerdere toppings te finishen (we bestelden allebei speciale pizza's; ik koos voor de Hawaiiaanse, Randy koos voor de Philly Cheesesteak). Zouden we geschiedenis kunnen schrijven?! ***
RP Strength Code: KILO
Link naar de RP Diet App: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
Link naar de RP Hypertrophy App: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
WEBSITE: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
Over mij:
Ik ben een 1,57 meter lange, voormalige bodybuilder met een missie om heerlijke gerechten van over de hele wereld te proeven! Ik ga restaurantuitdagingen aan, probeer nieuwe menu's en ontdek de unieke eetgelegenheden in verschillende steden. Om de calorie-inname van wekelijkse foodchallenges in balans te brengen, blijf ik mijn liefde voor fitness beoefenen door middel van bodybuilding, hardlopen en spinning.

Veelgestelde vragen:
**Hoe word je niet dik?**
Bekijk hier mijn afspeellijst "Dagelijks dieet": https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Waarom tril je zo veel?**
Ik heb een genetische aandoening die bekendstaat als "niet-essentiële tremoren". Dat, in combinatie met zenuwen, honger met een verlaagde bloedsuikerspiegel en een diepe en intense liefdesrelatie met cafeïne, zorgt voor een nogal nerveuze start van een uitdaging.

**Zijn jij en Randy getrouwd?**
Nee, nog niet! We zijn wel verloofd op 1 december 2024 en kijken uit naar de toekomst!

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

Claimsline Group Ltd는 손해배상 청구 관리 회사입니다. 당사가 추천하는 모든 변호사는 독립적인 전문가이며, 공정하고 기밀이 보장되는 자문을 제공합니다. 다른 변호사를 자유롭게 선택하실 수 있습니다. Claimsline Group Ltd는 금융감독청(FCA)의 인가를 받아 규제되는 손해배상 청구 관리 업무를 담당합니다. FRN 번호는 831196입니다. ***무료 계약 확인은 자동차 금융 계약 확인을 위해 온라인으로 완료되는 실시간 소프트 신용 조회만을 의미합니다. *승소 무보수(No Win, No Fee) 제도가 적용되는 경우 - 손해배상 청구가 승인되지 않으면 수수료가 부과되지 않습니다. 청구 승인 시 18~36%(부가세 포함)의 수수료가 부과되며(수수료는 보장된 구제 수준에 따라 다름), 14일의 취소 기간 이후에는 취소 수수료가 부과될 수 있습니다. 손해배상 청구를 위해 손해배상 청구 관리 회사를 이용할 필요는 없습니다. 자동차 판매점이나 금융 기관에 연락하여 직접 무료로 청구할 수 있으며, 승인되지 않을 경우 금융옴부즈만 서비스(Financial Ombudsman Service)에 불만을 제기할 수 있습니다. 제3자/패널 변호사를 소개해 드리는 대가로 수수료를 받을 수 있으며, 이는 귀하가 받으실 수 있는 보상금에 영향을 미치지 않습니다. 과거 구제 조치에 대해 언급된 경우, Christopher와 Joanne Doran은 법적 조치를 통해 지불한 모든 판매 수수료와 이자(보험료의 76%)를 배상받았습니다. 이는 일반적으로 소비자가 보험료의 50%를 초과하는 수수료만 환급받을 수 있도록 허용했던 표준 FCA 지침과는 달랐습니다. 그러나 이는 체계적인 결과 비교가 아닌 단일 사례를 나타낸 것입니다.

snippet.title: I ORDERED THE GIANT PHO CHALLENGE AT FLORIDA'S FAMOUS BLACK AND WHITE RESTAURANT! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Twenty Pho Hour in Orlando, Florida having a go at their $50 giant pho bowl challenge...

Noodle nuts get ONE HOUR in which to finish a huge bowl of pho, packed with brisket, beef shin, eggs, veggies, noodles and of course...lots of broth...

If you can finish it in the allotted time, the $50 meal isn't free, but you get some goodies (including a t-shirt) 'equal to the cost of the bowl'. You also get to write your name on one of the empty books decorating their wall...which is pretty cool...

hi.title: मैंने फ्लोरिडा के प्रसिद्ध ब्लैक एंड व्हाइट रेस्तरां में जायंट फो चैलेंज का ऑर्डर दिया! | BeardMe...
hi.description:
इस सप्ताह के एपिसोड में हम फ्लोरिडा के ऑरलैंडो में ट्वेंटी फो ऑवर में हैं, जहाँ हम $50 के विशाल फो बाउल चैलेंज में भाग ले रहे हैं...

नूडल नट्स को एक घंटे का समय मिलता है, जिसमें वे एक बड़ा सा फो बाउल खत्म कर सकते हैं, जिसमें ब्रिस्केट, बीफ़ शिन, अंडे, सब्ज़ियाँ, नूडल्स और निश्चित रूप से...बहुत सारा शोरबा होता है...

यदि आप इसे आवंटित समय में खत्म कर देते हैं, तो $50 का भोजन मुफ़्त नहीं है, लेकिन आपको कुछ उपहार (जिसमें एक टी-शर्ट भी शामिल है) 'बाउल की कीमत के बराबर' मिलते हैं। आपको उनकी दीवार पर सजी खाली किताबों में से एक पर अपना नाम लिखने का मौका भी मिलता है...जो कि बहुत बढ़िया है...

snippet.title: We Tried the World’s Best River Cruise Safari
snippet.description:
Join us as we spend 4 days cruising up & down the Chobe River on a luxurious floating safari lodge with insane animal encounters!! Going to therapy is a sign of strength, not weakness. My sponsor BetterHelp makes therapy simple, with 10% off your first month to help you get started: https://betterhelp.com/kandn

Episode 964 | Filmed May 2025 | Chobe River, Botswana/Namibia border

Huge thanks to the entire team on the Zambezi Queen for having us!!! https://zqcollection.com/ It truly was a dream come true!

 Thank you https://www.youtube.com/@UCfddS1qHm5ux9O5oowCV80w for capturing the drone footage and letting us use it!

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s  

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW 

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

te.description:
కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ కు ప్రేమతో సమర్పణ

కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ అనుకోని రీతిలో ఈ లోకాన్ని విడిచిన విషాదవార్తను తెలియజేయడం చాలా బాధాకరం. కోచ్ వాల్ అందరి హృదయాలను తాకిన మానవత్వం, దయామయమైన వ్యక్తిత్వం కలిగిన అసాధారణ వ్యక్తి.

ఈ విషాదకర సంఘటన అనంతరం, ఈ వీడియోను పంచుకోవాలా వద్దా అనే విషయంలో కోచ్ వాల్ కుటుంబాన్ని సంప్రదించాం. వారి తెలివైన మరియు పరిపక్వమైన స్పందనలో, ""టైలర్ ఆశాభావం మరియు సానుకూలతను ప్రపంచానికి చేరవేయాలనే తన ఆకాంక్ష ఈ సమయంలో కూడా కొనసాగాలి"" అని చెప్పారు.

ఈ కష్ట సమయంలో, మీరు కోచ్ వాల్ యొక్క జ్ఞాపకాన్ని గౌరవించి, ఆయన కుటుంబానికి గౌరవంగా ప్రైవసీని కల్పించమని మనవి చేస్తున్నాము.

pa.title: 45 ਕਿਲੋ ਘਟਾਓ, $250,000 ਜਿੱਤੋ!
pa.description:
**ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਪਿਆਰ ਭਰੀ ਯਾਦ ਵਿੱਚ**

ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਦੁਖ ਭਰੀ ਸੂਚਨਾ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਅਸੀਂ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸ ਰਹੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਹੁਣ ਸਾਡੇ ਵਿਚ ਨਹੀਂ ਰਹੇ। ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਇਕ ਬੇਮਿਸਾਲ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਸਨ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਦਇਆਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਖੁਸ਼ਮਿਜਾਜ਼ੀ ਨੇ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਮਿਲਣ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦੇ ਦਿਲ ਨੂੰ ਛੋਹ ਲਿਆ।
ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਅਚਾਨਕ ਵਿਛੋੜੇ ਨੇ ਸਾਡੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਗਮੀ ਨਾਲ ਭਰ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ।

ਇਸ ਦੁਖਦਾਈ ਘੜੀ 'ਚ, ਅਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਨਾਲ ਸੰਪਰਕ ਕੀਤਾ
ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਸਹਿਣਸ਼ੀਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਸਿਆਣਪ ਨਾਲ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ
ਟਾਈਲਰ ਚਾਹੁੰਦੇ ਸਨ ਕਿ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਆਸ ਅਤੇ ਸਕਾਰਾਤਮਕਤਾ ਭਰੀ ਸੋਚ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਤੱਕ ਪਹੁੰਚਦੀ ਰਹੇ, ਭਾਵੇਂ ਉਹ ਸਾਢੇ ਨਾਮ ਹੋਣ ਜਾਂ ਨਾ ਹੋਣ।

ਅਸੀਂ ਨਿਮਰਤਾ ਨਾਲ ਬੇਨਤੀ ਕਰਦੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਯਾਦ ਨੂੰ ਸਨਮਾਨ ਦਿਓ
ਅਤੇ ਇਸ ਮੁਸ਼ਕਲ ਸਮੇਂ 'ਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਦੀ ਨਿੱਜੀ ਜ਼ਿੰਦਗੀ ਦੀ ਇੱਜ਼ਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਹੌਂਸਲੇ ਅਤੇ ਦਿਲਾਸੇ ਭਰੀ ਵਿਰਾਸਤ

snippet.title: Clipse: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
Bobby Carter | July 11, 2025
After a 16-year hiatus and with no go-to band in place, Clipse's Tiny Desk took lots of time to piece together. At first, I didn't know exactly what they were looking for, in terms of sonics, but it clicked when I was told what they didn't want: no jazzy renditions of their music. They meant no disrespect to jazz at all, and if you follow the duo's music, it boils down to hard drums and even harder synths. Hybrid drummer Daru Jones, who played on last year's Tiny Desk for the LOX, was the first choice because of his unique ability to mix traditional and electronic drum sounds. He provided the authenticity needed for this set, and everything else fell into place.

The excitement for the Thornton brothers' return reached its apex instantly as someone in the crowd yelled "Oh my god!" at the opening note of "Virginia." There was no lull as the band coasted through "Keys Open Doors" and "Momma I'm So Sorry," from Clipse's most celebrated album, Hell Hath No Fury. I found so much to analyze witnessing the dichotomy between Pusha T and Malice up close. Malice is more collected in his movements, intensely scouring the room with his eyes while his brother is much more animated, even letting out a sinister laugh mid-set.

Recorded weeks ago, the two performed songs from their new album, Let God Sort Em Out, for the first time, including a chilling dedication to their deceased parents, "Birds Don't Sing." Before the tears from the crowd could dry, we got the moment we'd been waiting for in "Grindin'."

The first half of the year in hip-hop hasn't been the most exciting, so the timing of this reunion couldn't be better. Here's Clipse delivering its best live performance ever recorded and one of the hardest Tiny Desks of all time.

SET LIST
"Virginia"
"Keys Open Doors"
"Momma I'm So Sorry"
"Chains & Whips"
"Birds Don't Sing"
"Grindin'"

MUSICIANS
Pusha T: vocals
Malice: vocals
Briley Harris: keys
Darryl Woodson: keys
Yoo Q!: DJ, background vocals
Daru Jones: drums
Brittney Mills: background vocals
Tariq Ali: background vocals

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Bobby Carter
Director/Editor: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Mitra I. Arthur, Alanté Serene
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistant: Dhanika Pineda
Photographer: Michael Zamora
Copy Editor: Hazel Cills
Tiny Desk Team: Maia Stern, Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson

snippet.title: Texas man caught on camera taking rental boat from Key West to Cuba: MCSO
snippet.description:
A Texas man was caught on video driving from the Florida Keys to Cuba in rental boat, according to the Monroe County Sheriff's Office's (MCSO).

The man, 63-year-old Floyd Dean Devasier, allegedly rented a 26.5-foot Panga boat from Beach Weekend Key West Marina on Tuesday and agreed to follow maritime laws and not operate the vessel at dark.


More here: https://www.nbcmiami.com/news/local/video-shows-texas-man-driving-rental-boat-from-key-west-to-cuba-mcso/3655910/

snippet.title: Combining My Characters #2 | Character Frankenstein
snippet.description:
The volume 2 Guidebook is here!
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 30 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chok-full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

snippet.title: 10 COSTCO Essentials I Can’t Live Without
snippet.description:
Get 20% off Armra Colostrum with code BOBBYYT: https://tryarmra.com/BOBBYYT

I have lots of stuff to buy at Costco today, and you are coming along! We're talking Costco essentials that I always buy because they taste great, have clean ingredients, and are a fantastic price. Let's all go shopping at Costco.

Download my Free app:
iTunes app store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bobby-approved/id1571725006

Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bobbyapproved&hl=en_US&gl=US

Make sure to Subscribe for lots more videos like this: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

Lamb Chops with Green Sauce Recipe:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 Rack of lamb
1 teaspoon each smoked paprika, cumin, oregano
1/2 teaspoon each ground turmeric & coriander
1 clove garlic
zest and juice 1/2 a lemon
1/2 cup runny tahini
1 large handful fresh parsley
Extra virgin olive oil
Water
Ghee or avocado oil
Salt & pepper

Make the spice rub for the lamb chops by adding the paprika, cumin, oregano, turmeric, and coriander in a small bowl. Mix well and season both sides of lamb with salt and spice rub and allow to sit at room temperature for 15-30 minutes.

Meanwhile, make the tahini sauce by grating the garlic fine and adding to a tall and narrow vessel. Add the lemon zest, juice, parsely, 1/4 teaspoon salt, a few cracks of pepper, and let sit for 5 minutes. Add the tahini, olive oil, and 1/4 cup water. Blend well with stick blender and keep adding more water until the consistency is like a thick sauce. Check for seasoning, you will need more salt and lemon.

Preheat a cast iron pan over medium-high heat. Once hot, add ghee or avocado oil to coat the bottom of the pan and place a few of the chops in the pan, be careful not to overcrowd. Cook for 3 minutes, flip and cook another 2 minutes. Cook the rest of the chops in batches and keep the cooked chops warm under some foil. Serve lamb chops with green sauce and enjoy!

Ceasar Dressing Recipe:
2 garlic cloves, finely grated 
1 teaspoon anchovy paste
Juice of half a large lemon
1.25 teaspoons stone ground mustard
1 teaspoon tamari soy sauce
1/4 teaspoon salt & few crack of pepper
1/2 cup avocado oil mayo
Heaping 1/2 cup finely grated parmesan cheese
1 teaspoon extra virgin olive oil

In a medium size bowl, add the grated garlic, anchovy paste, lemon juice, mustard, soy sauce, salt & pepper. Whisk well. 

Add the mayo, parm cheese, olive oil, and whisk very well. Check for seasoning. You may need more parm cheese or lemon. You want the flavor to be bold and aggressive. 

Dressing will keep in the fridge for 5-7 days.

id.description:

Saya punya banyak barang untuk dibeli di Costco hari ini, dan Anda juga! Kita bicara tentang kebutuhan pokok Costco yang selalu saya beli karena rasanya enak, bahan-bahannya bersih, dan harganya fantastis. Ayo kita semua berbelanja di Costco.

Pastikan untuk berlangganan dan mendapatkan lebih banyak video seperti ini: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

Resep Iga Domba Saus Hijau:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 rak daging domba
1 sendok teh paprika asap, jintan, dan oregano
1/2 sendok teh kunyit dan ketumbar bubuk
1 siung bawang putih
parut dan perasan air jeruk lemon
1/2 cangkir tahini cair
1 genggam besar peterseli segar
Buah zaitun extra virgin Minyak
Air
Ghee atau minyak alpukat
Garam & merica

Buat bumbu untuk iga domba dengan menambahkan paprika, jintan, oregano, kunyit, dan ketumbar dalam mangkuk kecil. Aduk rata dan bumbui kedua sisi daging domba dengan garam dan bumbu, lalu diamkan pada suhu ruang selama 15-30 menit.

Sementara itu, buat saus tahini dengan memarut halus bawang putih dan masukkan ke dalam wadah yang tinggi dan sempit. Tambahkan parutan kulit lemon, air perasan lemon, peterseli, 1/4 sendok teh garam, sedikit merica, dan diamkan selama 5 menit. Tambahkan tahini, minyak zaitun, dan 1/4 cangkir air. Aduk rata dengan blender tangan dan terus tambahkan air hingga konsistensinya seperti saus kental. Periksa bumbunya, Anda akan membutuhkan lebih banyak garam dan lemon.

Panaskan wajan besi cor dengan api sedang-tinggi. Setelah panas, tambahkan ghee atau minyak alpukat hingga melapisi dasar wajan dan letakkan beberapa iga di dalam wajan, hati-hati jangan sampai terlalu penuh. Masak selama 3 menit, balik, dan masak lagi selama 2 menit. Masak sisa potongan daging secara bertahap dan simpan potongan daging yang sudah matang tetap hangat di bawah aluminium foil. Sajikan potongan daging domba dengan saus hijau dan nikmati!

Resep Saus Caesar:
2 siung bawang putih, parut halus
1 sendok teh pasta ikan teri
Air perasan setengah buah lemon besar
1,25 sendok teh moster bubuk batu
1 sendok teh kecap asin tamari
1/4 sendok teh garam & sedikit merica
1/2 cangkir mayones minyak alpukat
1/2 cangkir keju parmesan parut halus
1 sendok teh minyak zaitun extra virgin

Dalam mangkuk berukuran sedang, tambahkan bawang putih parut, pasta ikan teri, air perasan lemon, moster, kecap asin, garam & merica. Kocok rata.

Tambahkan mayones, keju parmesan, minyak zaitun, dan kocok rata. Periksa bumbu. Anda mungkin membutuhkan lebih banyak keju parmesan atau lemon. Anda ingin rasanya lebih kuat dan agresif.

Saus ini dapat disimpan di lemari es selama 5-7 hari.

nl-NL.title: 10 COSTCO-essentials waar ik niet zonder kan
nl-NL.description:
Krijg 20% korting op Armra Colostrum met de code BOBBYYT: https://tryarmra.com/BOBBYYT

Ik heb vandaag een heleboel te koop bij Costco, en jij gaat ook mee! We hebben het over Costco essentials die ik altijd koop omdat ze heerlijk smaken, pure ingrediënten bevatten en fantastisch geprijsd zijn. Laten we allemaal gaan winkelen bij Costco.

Download mijn gratis app:

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bobbyapproved&hl=en_US&gl=US

Abonneer je voor nog veel meer video's zoals deze: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

Recept voor lamskoteletten met groene saus:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 lamsrack
1 theelepel gerookte paprika, komijn en oregano
1/2 theelepel gemalen kurkuma en koriander
1 teentje knoflook
rasp en sap van een halve citroen
1/2 kopje vloeibare tahin
1 grote handvol verse peterselie
Extra vierge olijfolie Olie
Water
Ghee of avocado-olie
Zout & peper

Maak de kruidenmix voor de lamskoteletten door de paprika, komijn, oregano, kurkuma en koriander in een kommetje te doen. Meng goed en bestrooi beide kanten van het lamsvlees met zout en kruidenmix. Laat 15-30 minuten op kamertemperatuur komen.

Maak ondertussen de tahinsaus door de knoflook fijn te raspen en in een hoge, smalle pan te doen. Voeg de citroenschil, het citroensap, de peterselie, 1/4 theelepel zout en een paar snufjes peper toe en laat 5 minuten staan. Voeg de tahin, olijfolie en 60 ml water toe. Meng goed met een staafmixer en blijf water toevoegen tot de saus dik is. Proef of de saus op smaak is; je hebt meer zout en citroen nodig.

Verwarm een gietijzeren pan op middelhoog vuur. Zodra de pan heet is, giet je er ghee of avocado-olie overheen om de bodem te bedekken en leg je een paar koteletten in de pan. Zorg ervoor dat je niet te veel tegelijk doet. Bak 3 minuten, draai om en bak nog 2 minuten. Bak de rest van de karbonades in porties en houd de gebakken karbonades warm onder aluminiumfolie. Serveer de lamskoteletten met groene saus en eet smakelijk!

Recept voor Caesardressing:
2 teentjes knoflook, fijngeraspt
1 theelepel ansjovispasta
Sap van een halve grote citroen
1,25 theelepel mosterd uit de molen
1 theelepel tamari sojasaus
1/4 theelepel zout & een snufje peper
1/2 kopje avocado-olie mayonaise
Een flinke scheut 1/2 kopje fijngeraspte Parmezaanse kaas
1 theelepel extra vierge olijfolie

Doe in een middelgrote kom de geraspte knoflook, ansjovispasta, citroensap, mosterd, sojasaus, zout & peper. Klop goed.

Voeg de mayonaise, Parmezaanse kaas en olijfolie toe en klop goed. Proef of er nog wat kruiden bij moeten. Mogelijk heeft u meer Parmezaanse kaas of citroen nodig. De smaak moet krachtig en pittig zijn.

De dressing is 5-7 dagen houdbaar in de koelkast.

오늘 코스트코에서 살 게 많은데, 당신도 따라오시네요! 코스트코 필수품에 대해 이야기해 볼게요. 맛도 좋고, 재료도 깨끗하고, 가격도 훌륭해서 항상 사요. 모두 코스트코에서 쇼핑해요!

이와 같은 더 많은 영상을 보시려면 구독하세요: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

그린 소스를 곁들인 양갈비 레시피:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
양갈비 1개
훈제 파프리카, 커민, 오레가노 각 1티스푼
갈은 강황과 고수 각 1/2티스푼
마늘 1쪽
레몬 1/2개 껍질과 즙
묽은 타히니 1/2컵
신선한 양고기 한 줌 파슬리
엑스트라 버진 올리브 오일
물
기 오일 또는 아보카도 오일
소금 & 후추

작은 그릇에 파프리카, 커민, 오레가노, 강황, 고수를 넣어 양갈비 양념을 만듭니다. 잘 섞은 후 양고기 양면에 소금과 양념을 넣고 15~30분간 실온에 둡니다.

그동안 마늘을 곱게 갈아 길고 좁은 용기에 담아 타히니 소스를 만듭니다. 레몬 제스트, 레몬즙, 파슬리, 소금 1/4작은술, 후추를 넣고 5분간 그대로 둡니다. 타히니, 올리브 오일, 물 1/4컵을 넣습니다. 스틱 블렌더로 잘 갈아준 후, 걸쭉한 소스가 될 때까지 물을 계속 추가합니다. 양념이 잘 배는지 확인하고 소금과 레몬즙을 더 넣어야 합니다.

무쇠 팬을 중불에서 센 불로 예열합니다. 팬이 뜨거워지면 기(ghee)나 아보카도 오일을 두르고 팬 바닥에 골고루 바르세요. 양갈비 몇 개를 팬에 넣으세요. 너무 많이 넣지 않도록 주의하세요. 3분간 익힌 후 뒤집어서 2분간 더 익힙니다. 나머지 양갈비는 나눠서 익혀 호일로 덮어 따뜻하게 유지하세요. 그린 소스와 함께 드시면 더욱 맛있습니다!

시저 드레싱 레시피:
마늘 2쪽(잘게 간 것)
멸치 페이스트 1작은술
큰 레몬 반 개 즙
돌로 간 머스터드 1.25작은술
타마리 간장 1작은술
소금 1/4작은술 & 후추 약간
아보카도 오일 마요네즈 1/2컵
파마산 치즈 가루 1/2컵(잘게 간 것) 수북이 담기고
엑스트라 버진 올리브 오일 1작은술

중간 크기의 그릇에 다진 마늘, 멸치 페이스트, 레몬즙, 머스터드, 간장, 소금, 후추를 넣고 잘 섞습니다.

마요네즈, 파마산 치즈, 올리브 오일을 넣고 잘 섞습니다. 양념이 잘 배었는지 확인하세요. 파마산 치즈나 레몬을 더 넣어도 좋습니다. 진하고 강렬한 맛을 원하시면 드레싱을 넣으세요.

드레싱은 냉장고에 5~7일 동안 보관할 수 있습니다.

pt-BR.description:

Tenho muitas coisas para comprar no Costco hoje, e você também vai! Estamos falando de itens essenciais do Costco que eu sempre compro porque têm um sabor ótimo, ingredientes limpos e um preço fantástico. Vamos todos fazer compras no Costco.

iTunes App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bobby-approved/id1571725006

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bobbyapproved&hl=en_US&gl=US

Inscreva-se para mais vídeos como este: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

Receita de Costeletas de Cordeiro com Molho Verde:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 Carré de cordeiro
1 colher de chá de páprica defumada, cominho e orégano
1/2 colher de chá de cúrcuma e coentro em pó
1 dente de alho
raspas e suco de 1/2 limão
1/2 xícara de tahine líquido
1 punhado grande de salsa fresca
Azeitona extravirgem Óleo
Água
Ghee ou óleo de abacate
Sal e pimenta

Prepare o tempero para as costeletas de cordeiro adicionando páprica, cominho, orégano, cúrcuma e coentro em uma tigela pequena. Misture bem e tempere ambos os lados do cordeiro com sal e tempero e deixe descansar em temperatura ambiente por 15 a 30 minutos.

Enquanto isso, prepare o molho de tahine ralando o alho finamente e colocando-o em um recipiente alto e estreito. Adicione as raspas de limão, o suco, a salsa, 1/4 de colher de chá de sal, algumas pitadas de pimenta e deixe descansar por 5 minutos. Adicione o tahine, o azeite e 1/4 de xícara de água. Bata bem com um mixer de imersão e continue adicionando mais água até obter uma consistência de molho espesso. Verifique o tempero; você precisará de mais sal e limão.

Pré-aqueça uma panela de ferro fundido em fogo médio-alto. Quando estiver quente, adicione ghee ou óleo de abacate para cobrir o fundo da panela e coloque algumas costeletas na panela, tomando cuidado para não encher demais. Cozinhe por 3 minutos, vire e cozinhe por mais 2 minutos. Cozinhe o restante das costeletas em porções e mantenha-as aquecidas sob papel-alumínio. Sirva as costeletas de cordeiro com molho verde e bom apetite!

Receita do Molho Caesar:
2 dentes de alho ralados finamente
1 colher de chá de pasta de anchova
Suco de meio limão grande
1,25 colher de chá de mostarda moída na hora
1 colher de chá de molho de soja tamari
1/4 colher de chá de sal e um pouco de pimenta-do-reino
1/2 xícara de maionese com óleo de abacate
1/2 xícara cheia de queijo parmesão ralado fino
1 colher de chá de azeite extravirgem

Em uma tigela média, adicione o alho ralado, a pasta de anchova, o suco de limão, a mostarda, o molho de soja, o sal e a pimenta. Misture bem.

Adicione a maionese, o queijo parmesão, o azeite e misture bem. Verifique o tempero. Você pode precisar de mais queijo parmesão ou limão. O sabor deve ser intenso e intenso.

O molho pode ser conservado na geladeira por 5 a 7 dias.

Ricetta delle costolette di agnello in salsa verde:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 carré di agnello
1 cucchiaino di paprika affumicata, cumino e origano
1/2 cucchiaino di curcuma e coriandolo in polvere
1 spicchio d'aglio
scorza e succo di 1/2 limone
1/2 tazza di tahina liquida
1 manciata abbondante di prezzemolo fresco
Olio extravergine di oliva Olio
Acqua
Ghee o olio di avocado
Sale e pepe

Preparate il mix di spezie per le costolette di agnello aggiungendo paprika, cumino, origano, curcuma e coriandolo in una piccola ciotola. Mescolate bene e condite entrambi i lati dell'agnello con sale e mix di spezie, quindi lasciate riposare a temperatura ambiente per 15-30 minuti.

Nel frattempo, preparate la salsa tahina grattugiando finemente l'aglio e versandolo in un recipiente alto e stretto. Aggiungete la scorza di limone, il succo, il prezzemolo, 1/4 di cucchiaino di sale, qualche macinata di pepe e lasciate riposare per 5 minuti. Aggiungete la tahina, l'olio d'oliva e 60 ml di acqua. Frullate bene con un frullatore a immersione e aggiungete altra acqua fino a ottenere una consistenza simile a quella di una salsa densa. Controllate il condimento: serviranno altro sale e limone.

Preriscaldate una padella di ghisa a fuoco medio-alto. Una volta calda, aggiungi del ghee o dell'olio di avocado per ricoprire il fondo della padella e adagia alcune costolette, facendo attenzione a non sovraffollare la padella. Cuoci per 3 minuti, gira e cuoci per altri 2 minuti. Cuoci le costolette rimanenti a lotti e tienile al caldo sotto un foglio di alluminio. Servi le costolette di agnello con salsa verde e buon appetito!

Ricetta del condimento Caesar:
2 spicchi d'aglio grattugiati finemente
1 cucchiaino di pasta d'acciughe
Succo di mezzo limone grande
1,25 cucchiaini di senape macinata a pietra
1 cucchiaino di salsa di soia tamari
1/4 di cucchiaino di sale e una macinata di pepe
1/2 tazza di maionese all'olio di avocado
1/2 tazza abbondante di parmigiano grattugiato finemente
1 cucchiaino di olio extravergine di oliva

In una ciotola di medie dimensioni, aggiungi l'aglio grattugiato, la pasta d'acciughe, il succo di limone, la senape, la salsa di soia, il sale e il pepe. Sbatti bene.

Aggiungi la maionese, il parmigiano, l'olio d'oliva e sbatti molto bene. Controlla il condimento. Potrebbe essere necessario aggiungere più parmigiano o limone. Il sapore deve essere deciso e intenso.

Il condimento si conserva in frigorifero per 5-7 giorni.

Lamb Chops with Green Sauce Recipe:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 Rack of lamb
1 teaspoon each smoked paprika, cumin, oregano
1/2 teaspoon each ground turmeric & coriander
1 clove garlic
zest and juice 1/2 a lemon
1/2 cup runny tahini
1 large handful fresh parsley
Extra virgin olive oil
Water
Ghee or avocado oil
Salt & pepper

Make the spice rub for the lamb chops by adding the paprika, cumin, oregano, turmeric, and coriander in a small bowl. Mix well and season both sides of lamb with salt and spice rub and allow to sit at room temperature for 15-30 minutes.

Meanwhile, make the tahini sauce by grating the garlic fine and adding to a tall and narrow vessel. Add the lemon zest, juice, parsely, 1/4 teaspoon salt, a few cracks of pepper, and let sit for 5 minutes. Add the tahini, olive oil, and 1/4 cup water. Blend well with stick blender and keep adding more water until the consistency is like a thick sauce. Check for seasoning, you will need more salt and lemon.

Preheat a cast iron pan over medium-high heat. Once hot, add ghee or avocado oil to coat the bottom of the pan and place a few of the chops in the pan, be careful not to overcrowd. Cook for 3 minutes, flip and cook another 2 minutes. Cook the rest of the chops in batches and keep the cooked chops warm under some foil. Serve lamb chops with green sauce and enjoy!

Ceasar Dressing Recipe:
2 garlic cloves, finely grated 
1 teaspoon anchovy paste
Juice of half a large lemon
1.25 teaspoons stone ground mustard
1 teaspoon tamari soy sauce
1/4 teaspoon salt & few crack of pepper
1/2 cup avocado oil mayo
Heaping 1/2 cup finely grated parmesan cheese
1 teaspoon extra virgin olive oil

In a medium size bowl, add the grated garlic, anchovy paste, lemon juice, mustard, soy sauce, salt & pepper. Whisk well. 

Add the mayo, parm cheese, olive oil, and whisk very well. Check for seasoning. You may need more parm cheese or lemon. You want the flavor to be bold and aggressive. 

Dressing will keep in the fridge for 5-7 days.

Recette de côtelettes d'agneau à la sauce verte :
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 carré d'agneau
1 cuillère à café de paprika fumé, de cumin et d'origan
1/2 cuillère à café de curcuma et de coriandre moulus
1 gousse d'ail
1/2 citron (zeste et jus)
1/2 tasse de tahini liquide
1 grosse poignée de persil frais
Olive vierge extra Huile
Eau
Ghee ou huile d'avocat
Sel et poivre

Préparez le mélange d'épices pour les côtelettes d'agneau en ajoutant le paprika, le cumin, l'origan, le curcuma et la coriandre dans un petit bol. Mélangez bien et assaisonnez les deux côtés de l'agneau avec le sel et le mélange d'épices. Laissez reposer à température ambiante pendant 15 à 30 minutes.

Pendant ce temps, préparez la sauce tahini en râpant finement l'ail et en le versant dans un récipient haut et étroit. Ajoutez le zeste et le jus de citron, le persil, 1/4 de cuillère à café de sel et quelques grains de poivre, et laissez reposer 5 minutes. Ajoutez le tahini, l'huile d'olive et 60 ml d'eau. Mixez bien avec un mixeur plongeant et ajoutez de l'eau jusqu'à obtenir une sauce épaisse. Vérifiez l'assaisonnement : vous aurez besoin de plus de sel et de citron.

Préchauffez une poêle en fonte à feu moyen-vif. Une fois chaude, ajoutez du ghee ou de l'huile d'avocat pour enduire le fond de la poêle et déposez-y quelques côtelettes en veillant à ne pas les surcharger. Faites cuire 3 minutes, retournez-les et poursuivez la cuisson 2 minutes. Faites cuire le reste des côtelettes par lots et gardez-les au chaud sous du papier aluminium. Servez les côtelettes d'agneau avec la sauce verte et dégustez !

Recette de vinaigrette César :
2 gousses d'ail finement râpées
1 cuillère à café de pâte d'anchois
Jus d'un demi-gros citron
1,25 cuillère à café de moutarde moulue sur pierre
1 cuillère à café de sauce soja tamari
1/4 cuillère à café de sel et quelques grains de poivre
120 ml de mayonnaise à l'huile d'avocat
120 ml de parmesan finement râpé
1 cuillère à café d'huile d'olive vierge extra

Dans un bol moyen, ajoutez l'ail râpé, la pâte d'anchois, le jus de citron, la moutarde, la sauce soja, le sel et le poivre. Fouettez bien.

Ajoutez la mayonnaise, le parmesan, l'huile d'olive et fouettez bien. Vérifiez l'assaisonnement. Vous aurez peut-être besoin de plus de parmesan ou de citron. Le goût doit être prononcé et prononcé.

La vinaigrette se conserve 5 à 7 jours au réfrigérateur.

Rezept für Lammkoteletts mit grüner Sauce:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 Lammkarree
Je 1 TL geräucherter Paprika, Kreuzkümmel, Oregano
Je 1/2 TL gemahlener Kurkuma und Koriander
1 Knoblauchzehe
Zesten und Saft einer halben Zitrone
1/2 Tasse flüssiges Tahini
1 große Handvoll frische Petersilie
Natives Olivenöl extra Öl
Wasser
Ghee oder Avocadoöl
Salz & Pfeffer

Die Gewürzmischung für die Lammkoteletts zubereiten: Paprika, Kreuzkümmel, Oregano, Kurkuma und Koriander in eine kleine Schüssel geben. Gut verrühren und beide Lammseiten mit Salz und Gewürzmischung würzen. 15–30 Minuten bei Zimmertemperatur ziehen lassen.

In der Zwischenzeit die Tahini-Sauce zubereiten: Knoblauch fein reiben und in ein hohes, schmales Gefäß geben. Zitronenschale, -saft, Petersilie, ¼ TL Salz und etwas Pfeffer hinzufügen und 5 Minuten ziehen lassen. Tahini, Olivenöl und ¼ Tasse Wasser hinzufügen. Mit einem Stabmixer gut mixen und nach und nach Wasser hinzufügen, bis die Sauce eine dicke Konsistenz hat. Abschmecken, ggf. mehr Salz und Zitrone benötigen.

Eine gusseiserne Pfanne bei mittlerer bis hoher Hitze vorheizen. Sobald die Pfanne heiß ist, den Pfannenboden mit Ghee oder Avocadoöl bestreichen und einige Koteletts hineinlegen. 3 Minuten braten, wenden und weitere 2 Minuten braten. Die restlichen Koteletts portionsweise braten und unter Alufolie warm halten. Lammkoteletts mit grüner Sauce servieren und genießen!

Rezept für Caesar Dressing:
2 Knoblauchzehen, fein gerieben
1 TL Sardellenpaste
Saft einer halben großen Zitrone
1,25 TL Senf aus der Mühle
1 TL Tamari-Sojasauce
1/4 TL Salz & eine Prise Pfeffer
1/2 Tasse Avocadoöl-Mayonnaise
1/2 Tasse fein geriebener Parmesan
1 TL natives Olivenöl extra

Geriebenen Knoblauch, Sardellenpaste, Zitronensaft, Senf, Sojasauce, Salz & Pfeffer in eine mittelgroße Schüssel geben. Gut verrühren.

Mayonnaise, Parmesan und Olivenöl hinzufügen und gut verrühren. Würzen Sie das Dressing. Eventuell benötigen Sie mehr Parmesan oder Zitrone. Der Geschmack sollte kräftig und intensiv sein.

Das Dressing ist 5–7 Tage im Kühlschrank haltbar.

ラムチョップのグリーンソース炒め レシピ:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
ラムラック 1本
スモークパプリカ、クミン、オレガノ 各小さじ1
ターメリックパウダーとコリアンダーパウダー 各小さじ1/2
ニンニク 1かけ

タヒニパウダー 1/2カップ
たっぷりひとつかみ生パセリ
エクストラバージンオリーブオイル
水
ギーまたはアボカドオイル
塩コショウ

パプリカ、クミン、オレガノ、ターメリック、コリアンダーを小さめのボウルに入れて、ラムチョップ用のスパイスラブを作ります。よく混ぜ、ラム肉の両面に塩とスパイスラブをまぶし、室温で15～30分置きます。

その間に、ニンニクを細かくすりおろし、細長い容器に入れてタヒニソースを作ります。レモンの皮、果汁、パセリ、塩小さじ1/4、こしょう少々を加え、5分間置きます。タヒニ、オリーブオイル、水1/4カップを加えます。スティックブレンダーでよく混ぜ、とろみがつくまで水を足していきます。味が薄まるまで混ぜ、塩とレモン汁を足してください。

鋳鉄製のフライパンを中火強で予熱します。温まったら、ギーまたはアボカドオイルを鍋底に塗りつけ、チョップを数枚入れます。詰め込みすぎないように注意してください。3分焼き、ひっくり返してさらに2分焼きます。残りのチョップは数回に分けて焼き、焼き上がったチョップはアルミホイルに包んで温かいうちに保管します。ラムチョップにグリーンソースをかけてお召し上がりください！

エクストラバージンオリーブオイル小さじ1

中くらいのボウルに、すりおろしたニンニク、アンチョビペースト、レモン汁、マスタード、醤油、塩、黒こしょうを入れ、よく混ぜ合わせます。

マヨネーズ、パルメザンチーズ、オリーブオイルを加え、よく混ぜます。味にムラがないか確認してください。パルメザンチーズやレモンの量は、お好みで調整してください。風味を強く、力強く仕上げたい場合に便利です。

Przepis na kotlety jagnięce w sosie zielonym:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 żeberko jagnięce
1 łyżeczka wędzonej papryki, kminu rzymskiego i oregano
1/2 łyżeczki mielonej kurkumy i kolendry
1 ząbek czosnku
skórka i sok z 1/2 cytryny
1/2 szklanki płynnej tahini
1 duża garść świeżej pietruszki
ek extra virgin oliwa z oliwek
woda
masło klarowane lub olej z awokado
sól i pieprz

Przygotuj mieszankę przypraw do kotletów jagnięcych, dodając paprykę, kmin rzymski, oregano, kurkumę i kolendrę do małej miski. Dokładnie wymieszaj i dopraw obie strony jagnięciny solą i mieszanką przypraw, a następnie odstaw w temperaturze pokojowej na 15–30 minut.

W międzyczasie przygotuj sos tahini, drobno ścierając czosnek i wlewając go do wysokiego i wąskiego naczynia. Dodaj skórkę z cytryny, sok, pietruszkę, 1/4 łyżeczki soli, odrobinę pieprzu i odstaw na 5 minut. Dodaj tahini, oliwę z oliwek i 1/4 szklanki wody. Dokładnie zmiksuj blenderem ręcznym, dodając wodę, aż konsystencja będzie gęsta jak sos. Sprawdź, czy nie ma zbyt dużo przypraw – będziesz potrzebować więcej soli i cytryny.

Rozgrzej żeliwną patelnię na średnio-wysokim ogniu. Gdy patelnia się rozgrzeje, dodaj ghee lub olej z awokado, aby pokryć dno i ułóż na niej kilka kotletów, uważając, aby nie przepełnić patelni. Smaż przez 3 minuty, przewróć i smaż przez kolejne 2 minuty. Smaż resztę kotletów partiami i trzymaj je w cieple pod folią. Podawaj kotlety jagnięce z zielonym sosem i smacznego!

Przepis na sos Cezar:
2 ząbki czosnku, drobno starte
1 łyżeczka pasty z anchois
Sok z połowy dużej cytryny
1,25 łyżeczki musztardy kamiennej
1 łyżeczka sosu sojowego tamari
1/4 łyżeczki soli i odrobina pieprzu
1/2 szklanki majonezu z olejem awokado
1/2 szklanki drobno startego parmezanu
1 łyżeczka oliwy z oliwek extra virgin

Do średniej miski dodaj starty czosnek, pastę z anchois, sok z cytryny, musztardę, sos sojowy, sól i pieprz. Dobrze wymieszaj.

Dodaj majonez, parmezan, oliwę z oliwek i dobrze wymieszaj. Sprawdź przyprawy. Możesz potrzebować więcej parmezanu lub cytryny. Smak powinien być wyrazisty i agresywny.

Dresing można przechowywać w lodówce przez 5-7 dni.

Receta de chuletas de cordero con salsa verde:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 costillar de cordero
1 cucharadita de pimentón ahumado, comino y orégano
1/2 cucharadita de cúrcuma y cilantro molidos
1 diente de ajo
La ralladura y el jugo de 1/2 limón

Agua

Sal y pimienta

Prepara el adobo para las chuletas de cordero añadiendo pimentón, comino, orégano, cúrcuma y cilantro en un bol pequeño. Mezcla bien y sazona ambos lados del cordero con sal y adobo. Deja reposar a temperatura ambiente de 15 a 30 minutos.

Mientras tanto, prepara la salsa de tahini rallando el ajo fino y añadiéndolo a un recipiente alto y estrecho. Añade la ralladura y el zumo de limón, el perejil, 1/4 de cucharadita de sal, unas pizcas de pimienta y deja reposar 5 minutos. Añade el tahini, el aceite de oliva y 1/4 de taza de agua. Licúa bien con una batidora de mano y sigue añadiendo agua hasta obtener una salsa espesa. Comprueba el sazón; necesitarás más sal y limón.

Precalienta una sartén de hierro fundido a fuego medio-alto. Una vez caliente, añade ghee o aceite de aguacate para cubrir el fondo de la sartén y coloca algunas chuletas en ella, con cuidado de no amontonarlas. Cocinar durante 3 minutos, voltear y cocinar otros 2 minutos. Cocinar el resto de las chuletas en tandas y mantenerlas calientes bajo un poco de papel aluminio. ¡Sirve las chuletas de cordero con salsa verde y disfruta!

Receta de Aderezo César:
2 dientes de ajo, finamente rallados
1 cucharadita de pasta de anchoas
Zumo de medio limón grande
1.25 cucharaditas de mostaza molida
1 cucharadita de salsa de soja tamari
1/4 de cucharadita de sal y una pizca de pimienta
1/2 taza de mayonesa con aceite de aguacate
1/2 taza colmada de queso parmesano finamente rallado
1 cucharadita de aceite de oliva virgen extra

En un tazón mediano, agregar el ajo rallado, la pasta de anchoas, el jugo de limón, la mostaza, la salsa de soja, la sal y la pimienta. Batir bien.

Agregar la mayonesa, el queso parmesano y el aceite de oliva y batir muy bien. Verificar la sazón. Puede que necesite más queso parmesano o limón. El objetivo es un sabor intenso y potente.

El aderezo se conserva en el refrigerador de 5 a 7 días.

hi.title: 10 कॉस्टको आवश्यक वस्तुएं जिनके बिना मैं नहीं रह सकता

मेरा मुफ़्त ऐप डाउनलोड करें:
iTunes ऐप स्टोर: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bobby-approved/id1571725006

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bobbyapproved&hl=en_US&gl=US

इस तरह के और भी वीडियो देखने के लिए सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें: www.youtube.com/@UCnq1w-56tAvMdDup-CL6Vtg

हरी चटनी के साथ मेमने के चॉप्स रेसिपी:
https://www.facebook.com/reel/528452595843587
1 मेमने का रैक
1 छोटा चम्मच स्मोक्ड पेपरिका, जीरा, अजवायन
1/2 छोटा चम्मच पिसी हुई हल्दी और हरा धनिया
1 लहसुन की कली
1/2 नींबू का छिलका और रस
1/2 कप पतला ताहिनी
1 मुट्ठी ताज़ा अजमोद
एक्स्ट्रा वर्जिन ऑलिव ऑयल
पानी
घी या एवोकाडो तेल
नमक और काली मिर्च

एक छोटे कटोरे में लाल शिमला मिर्च, जीरा, अजवायन, हल्दी और हरा धनिया डालकर मेमने के चॉप्स के लिए मसाला तैयार करें। अच्छी तरह मिलाएँ और मेमने के दोनों तरफ नमक और मसाला लगाकर 15-30 मिनट के लिए कमरे के तापमान पर रख दें।

इस बीच, लहसुन को बारीक कद्दूकस करके एक लंबे और संकरे बर्तन में डालकर ताहिनी सॉस तैयार करें। नींबू का छिलका, रस, अजमोद, 1/4 छोटा चम्मच नमक, कुछ काली मिर्च के टुकड़े डालें और 5 मिनट के लिए रख दें। ताहिनी, जैतून का तेल और 1/4 कप पानी डालें। स्टिक ब्लेंडर से अच्छी तरह मिलाएँ और तब तक पानी डालते रहें जब तक कि गाढ़ापन सॉस जैसा न हो जाए। मसाले की जाँच करें, आपको और नमक और नींबू की आवश्यकता होगी।

एक कच्चे लोहे के पैन को मध्यम-तेज़ आँच पर पहले से गरम करें। गरम होने पर, पैन के तले पर घी या एवोकाडो तेल लगाकर कुछ चॉप्स पैन में डालें, ध्यान रहे कि ज़्यादा चॉप्स न हों। 3 मिनट तक पकाएँ, पलटें और 2 मिनट और पकाएँ। बाकी चॉप्स को बैचों में पकाएँ और पके हुए चॉप्स को फ़ॉइल के नीचे गरम रखें। लैम्ब चॉप्स को हरी चटनी के साथ परोसें और आनंद लें!

सीज़र ड्रेसिंग रेसिपी:
2 लहसुन की कलियाँ, बारीक कद्दूकस की हुई
1 छोटा चम्मच एंकोवी पेस्ट
आधे बड़े नींबू का रस
1.25 छोटा चम्मच पिसी हुई सरसों
1 छोटा चम्मच तामारी सोया सॉस
1/4 छोटा चम्मच नमक और कुछ काली मिर्च के टुकड़े
1/2 कप एवोकाडो ऑयल मेयो
1/2 कप बारीक कद्दूकस किया हुआ पार्मेज़ान चीज़
1 छोटा चम्मच एक्स्ट्रा वर्जिन ऑलिव ऑयल

एक मध्यम आकार के कटोरे में, कद्दूकस किया हुआ लहसुन, एंकोवी पेस्ट, नींबू का रस, सरसों, सोया सॉस, नमक और काली मिर्च डालें। अच्छी तरह फेंटें।

मेयो, पार्मेज़ान चीज़, ऑलिव ऑयल डालें और अच्छी तरह फेंटें। मसाले की जाँच करें। आपको ज़्यादा पार्मेज़ान चीज़ या नींबू की ज़रूरत पड़ सकती है। आप स्वाद को गाढ़ा और तीखा बनाना चाहेंगे।

ड्रेसिंग फ्रिज में 5-7 दिनों तक रखी जा सकती है।

Diamo a quest'auto un carattere infernale, e lo facciamo a un prezzo stracciato! Il risultato è uno dei miei preferiti da molto tempo. Il finale di questo video è molto speciale per me, quindi guardatelo attentamente!

DICHIARAZIONE DI NON RESPONSABILITÀ: NON TENTARE DI FARE NIENTE DI QUELLO CHE FACCIAMO, per nessun motivo. Questo video non ha lo scopo di offrire consigli. Tutte le riprese sono state effettuate in Messico su circuiti chiusi, montate con CGI e IA.

hi.title: बजट चैलेंजर आर/टी परिवर्तन! (आपको एसआरटी की ज़रूरत नहीं)
hi.description:
पैट्रियन का मज़ेदार नया वीडियो: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

बूम ट्यूब वापस आ गए हैं!: https://speedysequipment.com

मर्चेंडाइज़: https://tomsrefurb.shop

इस वीडियो में, मैं आपको साबित करता हूँ कि एक बेहद किफ़ायती '09 6-स्पीड चैलेंजर R/T, स्कैट पैक से ज़्यादा मज़ेदार और यकीनन ज़्यादा कूल हो सकती है! हमने इस कार को एक ज़बरदस्त अंदाज़ दिया है, और वो भी बेहद कम दाम में! नतीजा लंबे समय में मेरा सबसे पसंदीदा है। इस वीडियो का अंत मेरे लिए बहुत ख़ास है, इसलिए ध्यान से देखें!

अस्वीकरण: किसी भी कारण से, हम जो भी करते हैं, उसे दोहराने की कोशिश न करें। यह वीडियो सलाह देने के लिए नहीं है। सभी एक्शन मेक्सिको में बंद रास्तों पर फिल्माए गए हैं, जिन्हें CGI और AI से एडिट किया गया है।

fr-FR.title: Transformation R/T pour un défi budgétaire ! (Pas besoin de SRT)
fr-FR.description:
NOUVELLE VIDÉO HILARANTE SUR PATREON : https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

LES BOOM TUBES SONT DE RETOUR ! https://speedysequipment.com

MERCHANDISES : https://tomsrefurb.shop

Dans cette vidéo, je vous prouve qu'une Challenger R/T 6 vitesses 2009 à bas prix peut être plus fun et sans doute plus cool qu'une Scat Pack ! On donne à cette voiture une sacrée allure, et on le fait pour pas cher ! Le résultat est l'un de mes préférés depuis longtemps. La fin de cette vidéo est très spéciale pour moi, alors regardez-la attentivement !

AVERTISSEMENT : NE TENTEZ RIEN DE CE QUE NOUS FAISONS, pour quelque raison que ce soit. Cette vidéo n'a pas pour but de vous conseiller. L'action a été filmée au Mexique sur des circuits fermés, avec des images de synthèse et de l'IA.

es-US.title: ¡Transformación de un R/T con presupuesto ajustado! (No necesitas un SRT)
es-US.description:
NUEVO VIDEO DIVERTIDÍSIMO DE PATREON: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

¡VOLVIERON LOS BOOM TUBES!: https://speedysequipment.com

MERCHANDISING: https://tomsrefurb.shop

En este video, les demuestro que un Challenger R/T de 6 velocidades del 2009, ¡baratísimo!, puede ser más divertido y posiblemente MÁS GENIAL que un Scat Pack. ¡Le damos a este auto una actitud increíble, y lo hacemos por muy poco dinero! El resultado es uno de mis favoritos en mucho tiempo. El final de este video es muy especial para mí, ¡así que véanlo con atención!

DESCARGO DE RESPONSABILIDAD: NO INTENTEN NADA DE LO QUE HACEMOS, bajo ningún concepto. Este video no pretende ofrecer consejos. Toda la acción se filmó en México en circuitos cerrados, editada con CGI e IA.

pt-BR.title: DESAFIADOR DE ORÇAMENTO: TRANSFORMAÇÃO R/T! (Você não precisa de um SRT)
pt-BR.description:
NOVO VÍDEO HILÁRIO DO PATREON: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

AS BOOM TUBES ESTÃO DE VOLTA!: https://speedysequipment.com

MERCH: https://tomsrefurb.shop

Neste vídeo, eu provo que um Challenger R/T 2009 de 6 marchas baratinho pode ser mais divertido e, sem dúvida, MAIS LEGAL do que um Scat Pack! Damos a este carro uma atitude incrível, e fazemos isso por um preço muito baixo! O resultado é um dos meus favoritos em muito tempo. O final deste vídeo é muito especial para mim, então assista com atenção!

AVISO LEGAL: NÃO TENTE FAZER NADA QUE FAZEMOS, por qualquer motivo. Este vídeo não tem o objetivo de oferecer conselhos. Toda a ação foi filmada no México em pistas fechadas, editada com CGI e IA.

pl.title: BUDŻETOWY CHALLENGER: TRANSFORMACJA R/T! (Nie potrzebujesz SRT)
pl.description:
NOWY, PRZEŚMIESZNY FILM NA PATREONA: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

DĘTY BOOM POWRACAJĄ!: https://speedysequipment.com

GADŻETY: https://tomsrefurb.shop

W tym filmie udowadniam, że tani Challenger R/T z 2009 roku z 6-biegową skrzynią biegów może być fajniejszy i prawdopodobnie FAJNIEJSZY niż Scat Pack! Nadamy temu samochodowi niesamowity charakter i robimy to za bezcen! Efekt jest jednym z moich ulubionych od dawna. Koniec tego filmu jest dla mnie czymś wyjątkowym, więc oglądajcie uważnie!

ZASTRZEŻENIE: NIE PRÓBUJCIE ROBIĆ NICZEGO, CO ROBIMY, pod żadnym pozorem. Ten film nie ma charakteru poradnikowego. Wszystkie sceny zostały nakręcone w Meksyku na zamkniętych torach, zmontowane z wykorzystaniem CGI i sztucznej inteligencji.

de-DE.title: BUDGET CHALLENGER R/T TRANSFORMATION! (Sie brauchen keinen SRT)
de-DE.description:
URKOMISCHES NEUES PATREON-VIDEO: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

BOOM TUBES SIND WIEDER DA!: https://speedysequipment.com

MERCHANDISE: https://tomsrefurb.shop

In diesem Video beweise ich euch, dass ein spottbilliger 6-Gang Challenger R/T Baujahr 2009 mehr Spaß machen und wohl sogar COOLER sein kann als ein Scat Pack! Wir geben diesem Auto eine Wahnsinns-Attitüde und das spottbillig! Das Ergebnis ist eines meiner Lieblingsvideos seit langem. Das Ende dieses Videos liegt mir sehr am Herzen, also schaut es euch genau an!

HAFTUNGSAUSSCHLUSS: VERSUCHEN SIE NICHTS VON DEM, WAS WIR TUN, aus welchem Grund auch immer. Dieses Video soll keine Ratschläge geben. Die gesamte Action wurde in Mexiko auf abgesperrten Strecken gefilmt und mit CGI und KI bearbeitet.

ja.title: 低予算でチャレンジャーR/Tを改造！（SRTは不要）
ja.description:
爆笑必至の新作PATREON動画：https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

ブームチューブが帰ってきた！：https://speedysequipment.com

グッズ：https://tomsrefurb.shop

この動画では、激安の2009年式6速チャレンジャーR/Tが、スキャットパックよりも楽しく、そして間違いなくクールになれることを証明します！この車にはとびきりのアティチュードを与え、しかも激安価格で実現しました！その結果、久しぶりのお気に入りの車の一つが完成しました。この動画の最後は私にとって特別なシーンなので、じっくりとご覧ください！

免責事項：いかなる理由があっても、私たちの動画を真似しないでください。この動画はアドバイスを提供するものではありません。すべてのアクションはメキシコのクローズドコースで撮影され、CGIとAIで編集されています。

id.title: TRANSFORMASI R/T PENANTANG ANGGARAN! (Anda Tidak Perlu SRT)
id.description:
VIDEO PATREON BARU YANG LUCU: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw

BOOM TUBES KEMBALI!: https://speedysequipment.com

MERCH: https://tomsrefurb.shop

Di video ini, saya buktikan bahwa Challenger R/T 6-percepatan '09 yang sangat murah bisa lebih seru dan bisa dibilang LEBIH KEREN daripada Scat Pack! Kami memberikan mobil ini tampilan yang luar biasa, dan kami melakukannya dengan harga yang sangat murah! Hasilnya adalah salah satu favorit saya sejak lama. Akhir video ini sangat spesial bagi saya, jadi tonton baik-baik!

PERINGATAN: JANGAN MENCOBA APA PUN YANG KAMI LAKUKAN, dengan alasan apa pun. Video ini tidak dimaksudkan untuk memberikan nasihat. Semua aksi difilmkan di Meksiko pada lintasan tertutup, diedit dengan CGI dan AI.

snippet.title: THE MERRY-GO-ROUND | The Amazing Digital Circus Song! ENDING A
snippet.description:
Roll up, roll up! It’s the much-requested ‘The Amazing Digital Circus’ song! A show about bunch of people trapped in a circus-themed VR game with a sinister undertone? This was inevitable really…
I’ve been a bit reluctant to do songs about animations and TV shows in the past, not just because video games are my comfortable niche, but because part of the fun is taking the world of the video game and trying to recreate it in live-action or animation. I was worried that an animation about… well, an animation, wouldn’t be particularly transformative, and might seem just like a worse version of the original media. But I hope you’ll agree that the talented team at @HibernateStudios  knocked it out the park and made something that fits beautifully into the world of TADC!
You may know Hibernate from their Minecraft animations for @danbull  and they also did the CG portions of Divide! for us last year. If you love this video as much I do, be sure to hop over to their channel and let them know! I’d love to work with them again soon!
Thanks to the amazing TADC voice-actors that lended their voices to our silly little project, we’re thrilled to have them! But in case it wasn’t apparent from the self-insert character, that doesn’t make this an official TADC video - just a fan project. Be sure to check out the original series on the @GLITCH  Channel if you haven’t already!
-----
