snippet.title: Por Sus Besos - Tito Double P (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
•ESCUCHA AQUÍ
https://orcd.co/porsusbesos

•LETRA:
Ay mama!
Tito doble P

Ya no se ni donde estoy
Le estoy marcando y me manda al buzón
Estaba en línea y ni me contestó
Su amiga me dice que ya se durmió
Pero no le creo nada
Siempre es la misma cuando anda tomada
Apaga el cel, dice que no pasa nada
y yo ando que me lleva la chingada

Por sus besos
Por su cuerpo
Por su voz
Por su tiempo
Por supuesto por su amor
¿Cómo es eso,
Que todo se te olvidó?
Ya ni siento
Traigo roto el corazón

Ay mama
Ahi te va chiquita
Y el balero mija?

Ya ni se pa donde voy
Sigo soñando con tu habitación
Que feo estar solo en el mes del amor
Y tú sigues sin contestar el fon
Solo en la madrugada
Que ando bien loco dice la plebada
Para dormir me haces falta aquí en mi cama

Hoy quiero que me lleve la chingada
Por sus besos
Por su cuerpo
Por su voz
Por su tiempo
Por supuesto por su amor
¿Cómo es eso
Que todo se te olvidó?
Ya ni siento
Tengo roto el corazón

Tito Double P

snippet.title: "Dream Come True" Music Video! ⭐️ | ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires | @disneychannelmusic
snippet.description:
Watch the "Dream Come True" music video from ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires! Performed by Malachi Barton and Freya Skye.

ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires available on Disney Channel and Disney+
https://ondisneyplus.disney.com/movie/zombies-4-dawn-of-the-vampires

Watch the next music video from ZOMBIES 4: Dawn of the Vampires here: https://youtu.be/NdOO9DLkwVo

Watch ZOMBIES 4 on Disney Channel! And check out more ZOMBIES 4 content here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHAfvwqfR5OA47WZB3-79ORi1SjVfbnzB

Check out more Disney ZOMBIES videos here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiv1IUQDVSNK24tqIxEQUmKxFnqkp3Dud&si=ZcRORW673WUk3OTP

"Zombies 4" introduces two warring groups of monsters, Daywalkers and Vampires, who inhabit two spectacular new worlds: east and west Rayburn, a world of perpetual day and a world of perpetual night. It’s up to Zed and Addison to help these two groups of sworn enemies find peace and common ground before their worlds suffer catastrophic consequences.

"Descendants/Zombies: Worlds Collide Tour" is a one-of-a-kind interactive live concert experience coming to arenas across North America in Summer 2025. The tour will feature Kylie Cantrall, Freya Skye, Malia Baker, Malachi Barton, Dara Reneé, Joshua Colley and Mekonnen Knife.  Kicking off in San Diego, CA on July 17, the arena tour will celebrate the chart-topping music from Disney’s “Descendants” and “Zombies” movie franchises, inspiring families, and fans of all ages to dance, sing, and engage with their favorite stars. 

#disneyzombies #zombies4 #disneychannel #disneychannelmusic

snippet.title: F4 x MAYDAY五月天 [ 流星雨 Meteor Rain ] 5525版 Official Stage Video
snippet.description:
一場橫跨24年的青春盛宴
一首〈流星雨〉喚醒全亞洲的共同記憶
​
華語最強傳奇男團 —— F4
亞洲第一搖滾天團 —— 五月天 
神級合體，震撼降臨臺北大巨蛋
重啟《流星花園》席捲全亞洲的青春風暴
​
陪你去看流星雨，
陪你一起把奇蹟變現場
讓不可能在此刻發生！

／

♛ F4
華語第一傳奇男團，橫掃亞洲的青春現象級符號
朱孝天、言承旭、吳建豪、周渝民
以《流星花園》紅遍全亞洲，成名於世，更登上《富比士》，接受《CNN》專訪
被譽為「亞洲之光」的國際級偶像傳奇！
​
♛ MAYDAY 五月天
全亞洲最具代表性的搖滾天團，世代共鳴的象徵
阿信（Vocal)、怪獸（Guitar）、石頭（Guitar）、瑪莎（Bass）、冠佑（Drum）
巡演足跡遍及亞洲、美洲、歐洲與澳洲
征服全球多座指標性舞台，將華語搖滾刻進世界音樂版圖
美國《華盛頓郵報》盛讚為「華人披頭四」
亞洲媒體一致推崇的——「演唱會之王」！

​
／
​
MAYDAY #5525 LIVE TOUR
五月天 [ 回到那一天 ] 25週年巡迴演唱會
​
一生必看一場五月天！
🏆 橫掃 8 項國際舞台設計大獎
🏆 15,640 片 16K 巨型球體 LED，震撼視覺極限
🏆 斥資 2,600 萬美金，締造全感官極致舞台
🏆 螢光棒智慧連控燈效，共創沉浸式萬人圖騰秀
​
91場巡演，380萬人次熱血共鳴
雙主題、雙體驗，全方位升級感官震撼
2025盛夏，五月天即將締造北京鳥巢42場新紀錄
寫下華語樂壇前所未見、最傳奇的一頁！
​

#F4 #五月天 #MAYDAY
#MAYDAY5525LIVETOUR
#Concert #LiveTour

-

▍流星雨 Meteor Rain｜5525版
▍F4 X 五月天｜回到那一天

作詞｜鄔裕康     作曲｜平井堅

陪你去看流星雨  落在這地球上 
讓你的淚落在我肩膀
要你相信我的愛  只肯為你勇敢 
你會看見  幸福的所在

讓你的淚落在我肩膀
要你相信我的愛  只肯為你勇敢 
你會看見  幸福的所在

傷感若太多  心丟給我保護 
疲倦的煙火  我會替你都趕走
燦爛的言語  只能點綴感情 
如果我沉默  因為我真的愛你

牽你手  跟著我走  風再大又怎樣 
你有了我  再也不會迷路方向

陪你去看流星雨  落在這地球上 
讓你的淚落在我肩膀
要你相信我的愛  只肯為你勇敢 
你會看見  幸福的所在

雨和雲漸漸散開   灑下一片溫暖 
我要分享你眼中的淚光

snippet.title: 'Love Island USA': Ace Dishes On If He's The Group Leader & Confirms His HEIGHT
snippet.description:
Ace Greene and Chelley Bissainthe's time on "Love Island USA" may be over, but the two already feel like winners! The pair talked to Access Hollywood after their shocking elimination and confirmed they will continue to date outside the villa. The two also shut down rumors that they were dating before they got on the show. Ace and Chelley also weighed in on if they think Nic and Olandria actually have a romantic spark and revealed if they think fellow islanders had ulterior motives when voting people out. snippet.title: FATAL FURY: CotW × STREET FIGHTER｜KEN
snippet.description:
Ken from Street Fighter brings the heat to FATAL FURY: City of the Wolves this summer! 

■ Fatal Fury x Street Fighter: The dream crossover!
Ken and Chun-Li from Capcom's renowned fighting game franchise Street Fighter are coming to FATAL FURY: City of the Wolves! Their inclusion amounts to a legendary crossover like no other, as Fatal Fury's own Terry Bogard and Mai Shiranui are already on the Street Fighter 6 roster. Ken and Chun-Li join City of the Wolves as part of Season Pass 1, with Ken arriving in Summer 2025 and Chun-Li in Winter 2025.

■ KEN (Voice Actors: David Matranga)
A veteran Metro City street fighter who sets his sights on South Town, seeking closure for an incident to which he was wrongfully tied. Burning with determination and a fiery arsenal of unmatched offense, this former US National Fighting Champion eventually crosses paths with the Legendary Wolf himself—and with that, the wheels of fate are set in motion.
